---
import Icon from '../Icon.astro';
---

<section id="safety" class="py-16 sm:py-24 lg:py-32 bg-dark-bg overflow-hidden relative parallax-container">

  <!-- Ambient glow -->
  <div class="absolute -top-40 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-[400px] sm:w-[600px] h-[400px] sm:h-[600px] rounded-full bg-hero-accent/5 blur-[100px] pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true"></div>

  <!-- Bike silhouette watermark (desktop only) -->
  <div class="absolute right-0 bottom-0 opacity-[0.025] pointer-events-none hidden xl:block" aria-hidden="true">
    <svg viewBox="0 0 520 300" width="600" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
      <circle cx="130" cy="230" r="65" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="8"/>
      <circle cx="390" cy="230" r="65" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="8"/>
      <path d="M 230 200 L 200 130 L 280 100 L 360 130 L 390 165" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="10" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
      <path d="M 280 100 Q 350 70 410 90 Q 430 100 420 120 L 390 165 L 360 130 Z" fill="white"/>
    </svg>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
    <div class="text-center mb-12 sm:mb-16 lg:mb-24">
      <div class="section-divider mx-auto reveal"></div>
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-7xl xl:text-8xl font-black italic tracking-tighter uppercase mb-4 sm:mb-6 reveal">
        The Dual-Layer <span class="text-hero-accent">Safety Net</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-dark-text-secondary max-w-2xl mx-auto uppercase tracking-wider text-xs sm:text-sm font-bold reveal" style="transition-delay:150ms">
        Whether you're on a solo commute or a cross-country tour, help is always one signal away.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-6 sm:gap-10 lg:gap-14">

      <!-- Group Riders card -->
      <article
        id="safety-group"
        class="glass-panel p-6 sm:p-10 relative overflow-hidden group hover:-translate-y-2 sm:hover:-translate-y-3 transition-all duration-500 cursor-default reveal-left"
        style="border-color: rgba(47,107,255,0.25); animation: glow-border 4s ease-in-out infinite;"
      >
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-hero-accent via-hero-accent/60 to-transparent"></div>
        <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500 bg-gradient-to-br from-hero-accent/5 to-transparent pointer-events-none"></div>
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-4 sm:p-8 opacity-[0.07] group-hover:opacity-[0.12] transition-opacity duration-500" aria-hidden="true">
          <Icon name="users" size={100} class="text-hero-accent sm:hidden" />
          <Icon name="users" size={140} class="text-hero-accent hidden sm:block" />
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 sm:gap-4 mb-6 sm:mb-8">
          <div class="p-3 sm:p-4 bg-hero-accent/10 rounded-full group-hover:bg-hero-accent/20 transition-colors duration-300 relative shrink-0">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 rounded-full border border-hero-accent/30 animate-radar"></div>
            <div class="absolute inset-0 rounded-full border border-hero-accent/20 animate-radar" style="animation-delay: 1s;"></div>
            <Icon name="shield" size={24} class="w-6 h-6 sm:w-8 sm:h-8 text-hero-accent relative z-10" />
          </div>
          <span class="text-[10px] font-mono tracking-widest uppercase opacity-50">Mode: Pack Synchronization</span>
        </div>

        <h3 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-black italic uppercase mb-4 sm:mb-6 tracking-tighter group-hover:text-hero-accent transition-colors duration-300">For Group Riders</h3>
        <p class="text-dark-text-secondary mb-6 sm:mb-8 text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed">
          In the event of a crash, every member in your group receives <strong class="text-dark-text-primary">instant, high-priority alerts</strong> with exact GPS coordinates. Friends become first responders.
        </p>

        <div class="border-t border-dark-border pt-6 sm:pt-8">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-success font-bold uppercase text-xs tracking-widest">
            <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-success animate-pulse shrink-0"></span>
            Immediate Support Protocol
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- Solo Riders card -->
      <article
        id="safety-solo"
        class="glass-panel p-6 sm:p-10 relative overflow-hidden group hover:-translate-y-2 sm:hover:-translate-y-3 transition-all duration-500 cursor-default reveal-right"
        style="border-color: rgba(194,59,34,0.2);"
      >
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-danger via-danger/60 to-transparent"></div>
        <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500 bg-gradient-to-br from-danger/5 to-transparent pointer-events-none"></div>
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-4 sm:p-8 opacity-[0.07] group-hover:opacity-[0.12] transition-opacity duration-500 text-white" aria-hidden="true">
          <Icon name="navigation" size={100} class="sm:hidden" />
          <Icon name="navigation" size={140} class="hidden sm:block" />
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 sm:gap-4 mb-6 sm:mb-8">
          <div class="p-3 sm:p-4 bg-danger/10 rounded-full group-hover:bg-danger/20 transition-colors duration-300 relative shrink-0">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 rounded-full border border-danger/30 animate-radar"></div>
            <div class="absolute inset-0 rounded-full border border-danger/20 animate-radar" style="animation-delay: 1s;"></div>
            <Icon name="bell" size={24} class="w-6 h-6 sm:w-8 sm:h-8 text-danger relative z-10" />
          </div>
          <span class="text-[10px] font-mono tracking-widest uppercase opacity-50">Mode: Solo Sentry</span>
        </div>

        <h3 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-black italic uppercase mb-4 sm:mb-6 tracking-tighter group-hover:text-danger transition-colors duration-300">For Solo Riders</h3>
        <p class="text-dark-text-secondary mb-6 sm:mb-8 text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed">
          Accident detected? Rydal triggers an <strong class="text-dark-text-primary">Automatic Emergency SOS</strong>, sending your live location to pre-set contacts via SMS and Data. No rider is ever truly alone.
        </p>

        <div class="border-t border-dark-border pt-6 sm:pt-8">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-danger font-bold uppercase text-xs tracking-widest">
            <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-danger animate-ping shrink-0"></span>
            Emergency Broadcast Protocol
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
